OL,3,CJersey Zoo board survive historic no
OL,4,Cconfidence vote
OL,6,FBoard of Trustees have survived a vote
OL,7,Fof no confidence.
OL,9,FThe result of a members' ballot was
OL,10,Fannounced at the first 'Extraordinary
OL,11,FGeneral Meeting' (EGM) in the
OL,12,Forganisation's history on Thursday
OL,13,Fevening (2 May).
OL,15,F2,785 votes were cast in person or via
OL,16,Fproxy with 710 calling for the board
OL,17,Fto be ousted and 1,985 supporting them
OL,18,F- there were 90 absentations.
OL,20,FIt means there will be no immediate
OL,21,Fchanges to the Board of Trustees.
