OL,3,CJersey Zoo board survive historic no
OL,4,Cconfidence vote
OL,6,FApproximately 16,000 members were
OL,7,Feligible to vote, giving a turnout of
OL,8,Faround 17%.
OL,10,FThe EGM took place after of the
OL,11,FDurrell Wildlife Conservation Trust
OL,12,Fwhich runs Jersey Zoo stated they had
OL,13,F"lost confidence in the board's
OL,14,Fability to protect and maintain the
OL,15,Flegacy of Gerald Durrell", the zoo's
OL,16,Ffounder.
OL,18,FIt came amid allegations that animals
OL,19,Fare not cared for properly and workers
OL,20,Fare being bullied as part of a "toxic
OL,21,Fworkplace" culture with .
