OL,3,CJersey Zoo board survive historic no
OL,4,Cconfidence vote
OL,6,FHowever, Chair of Trustees Matthew
OL,7,FHatchwell said the organisation had
OL,8,F"done everything" to address concerns
OL,9,Fand Jersey's Chief Vet found no issues
OL,10,Fduring an inspection in September 2023.
OL,12,FIn an email to members following the
OL,13,Fresult, Mr Hatchwell stated: "Starting
OL,14,Fnow, our top priority is to rebuild
OL,15,Ftrust and unity of purpose within
OL,16,FDurrell, which is vital as we look to
OL,17,Fthe future, to plan our next
OL,18,Fconservation strategy and build on
OL,19,FGerald Durrell's legacy of saving
OL,20,Fspecies from extinction."
